We neglect full hydrodynamic interactions, vÌ‡ âˆ¼ 0, and, therefore, the hydrodynamic contribution is reduced to FH = âˆ’Î³ v, i.e., the Stokes drag of an isolated particle, where Î³ = 6Ï€Î·a is
